## ğŸ§ª Example Usage

```python
from disco_tools.label_selector import Label, qualifies

rule = (Label("env") == "prod") + Label("version").gte(10)
meta = {"env": "prod", "version": 12}

if qualifies(meta, rule):
    print("Match!")
```

